sun.misc

Class Unsafe

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.misc.Unsafe

  • public class Unsafe
extends Object
    Unsafe = unwanted. See comments in the native peer. We only have it because it is required by java.util.concurrent. Note that in the real world, this class is only callable from the system library, not application code
